title: Bon Jovi - Livin' On A Prayer
description: "Livin' on a Prayer" is Bon Jovi's second chart-topping single from their 12Ã— platinum Slippery When Wet album. Written by Jon Bon Jovi, Richie Sambora, and Desmond Child, the single, released in late 1986, was well received at both rock and pop radio and its music video was given heavy rotation at MTV, giving the band their first No. 1 on the Billboard Mainstream Rock chart and their second consecutive No. 1 Billboard Hot 100 hit
